<h1>Tokyo</h1>
    <p>Tokyo, Japan, is a dynamic global city that serves as the nation's capital and its political, financial, and cultural hub.</p>
    <p>It blends tradition and modernity, offering everything from historic temples in areas like Asakusa to futuristic skyscrapers in districts like Shinjuku, while also being a renowned global hub for dining and shopping, particularly in trendy areas like Shibuya and luxury spots like Ginza.  </p>
 